<p>Despite the fact that the children had labored with such vigor that the robust arboreal giants refused to surrender to the incipient conflagration, the careful hiker’s cigarette, which had been inadvertently ignited within the barren underbrush, nevertheless managed to kindle a flame that, while lacking an uncomplicated trajectory, was ultimately restrained by the timely arrival of the rangers, who, upon assessing the situation, determined that the fire’s potential to proliferate had been sufficiently mitigated before it could escape the confines of its initial, albeit unpredictable, origin.</p>